page.title: 08WARREN FARM
page.content: Warren Farm is in Morestead.It belongs to Sir Dennis Mountain. The Egerton faimly live on the farm in a cottage that is about a hundred years old. Sir Dennis owns around two hundred fresian cows,and two fresian bulls.There are eight workers on Warren Farm.Warren Farm grows grass for the cows.They have four fields of corn.Warren Farm has some ditches. Warren Farm has six tractors,a J.C.B. and a three ton roller,three combine harvesters,four trailers, a plough, a silage harvester and a silage cutter. Warren Farm no longer has a gamekeeper as he now works at a bigger farm where he gets paid more money.
